## Inspection Complete

Created `docs/redesign/inspection-report.md` with full project analysis.

### Key Findings

**Project:** Vite + React 19 + Tailwind CSS v4, pnpm monorepo with `apps/web` + 10 packages.

**Routes:** 25+ mapped. 15+ missing routes needed per spec (`/tutor`, `/practice`, `/saved`, `/settings/*`, etc.).

**Theme System:** Existing CSS custom properties (220 lines) + TypeScript tokens — decent foundation but missing ~50+ tokens (surface variants, vocabulary/grammar/band colors, animation keyframes, softer shadows, warm backgrounds).

**Components:** 19 UI components exist. Need ~20 new (SearchInput, Tabs, ProgressBar, ProgressRing, SkillCard, StudyTaskCard, AITutorMessageCard, etc.) and 16 refinements.

**Hard-coded values found in:** `Settings.tsx`, `ReviewCenter.tsx`, `StudyPlan.tsx`, `AITutorChat.tsx`, `Dashboard.tsx` — raw Tailwind color classes mixed with CSS variable approach.

**Duplicated patterns:** `IELTS_TOPICS` in 2 files, `getTimeBasedGreeting()` in 2 files, skill configs in 3+ places, `features/studyPlan/` vs `features/study-plan/` directories.

### Implementation Plan (19 Phases)

0. Theme token enhancement
1. Component system redesign
2. Layout & navigation redesign
3. Landing page → 4. Onboarding → 5. Dashboard → 6. Study Plan → 7. Roadmap → 8. AI Tutor → 9. Vocabulary → 10. Practice pages → 11. Saved Content → 12. Mistakes → 13. Progress → 14. Settings → 15. Extension → 16-19. States/Responsive/Accessibility/Dark mode

Ready to proceed with Phase 0 (theme tokens) when you are.
